<sect1 id="index_1autotoc_md1">
<title>Overview</title>
<para><computeroutput>shgui</computeroutput> is a very simple and lightweight ui system for <computeroutput>Vulkan</computeroutput> applications written completely in C.</para>
<para>It is designed to facilitate the creation and management of basic graphical user interface elements in applications. It offers a straightforward set of functions and structures to simplify GUI development within Vulkan-based projects.</para>
