<sect1 id="index_1autotoc_md2">
<title>Available widgets</title>
<para>Developers can use the shgui library to quickly incorporate basic gui elements, such as text rendering, into their c-based applications. It simplifies the process of displaying windows, characters and text on graphical surfaces, making it ideal for projects requiring simple user interface components without complex dependencies.</para>
